경희대학교 외래교수 - 전) 청구경희한의원 원장 - 전) 경희대학교 겸임교수 - 척추 신경추나의학회 회원 - 대한응용근신...</p>\n                                        <p class=\"se-oglink-url\">booking.naver.com</p>\n                                    </div>\n                                </a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module='{\"type\":\"v2_oglink\", \"id\" :\"SE-aa20662c-92ef-4e5b-bb1f-912791ce2ffe\", \"data\" : {\"link\" : \"https://booking.naver.com/booking/13/bizes/331349\", \"isVideo\" : \"false\", \"thumbnail\" : \"https://dthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/?src&#x3D;%22https%3A%2F%2Fldb-phinf.pstatic.net%2F20210929_209%2F1632881933870CLTDM_JPEG%2F%25C0%25CC%25BC%25F6_%25C7%25C3%25B7%25B9%25C0%25CC%25BD%25BA_%25BD%25E61.jpg%3Ftype%3Df804_408_60_sharpen%22&amp;type&#x3D;ff500_300\"}}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5537b33e-ea3c-4041-b9d7-4da306fb35b8\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-268AE211-02E2-4602-8888-0F13AD786590\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-75B1AD22-54A8-4C36-B352-E01B80C6C1C1\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>    </div>",
